{"title":"Trastorno_Afectivo_Bipolar_TAB","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Psiquiatría/Trastorno_Afectivo_Bipolar_TAB.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"TRASTORNO AFECTIVO BIPOLAR (TAB)","guid":"UlG4G8w7QQqO2oJyyDfwfQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definición y Clasificación","guid":"0JPbWMbTTQOyefZb_xTmKA","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Enfermedad mental grave, crónica y recurrente","guid":"X9T989WZQf6lu0EmTyWTHA","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Episodios de manía, hipomanía y depresión alternados con eutimia","guid":"gOC2bfJ5RrqxC4DOTcfF3w","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Afecta ánimo, cognición, funcionalidad y ciclo vital","guid":"LMkAnfgJSc-wTCqPnY8vQQ","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Clasificación DSM-5-TR","guid":"4a6tTVpMT7-RmnaTJ-HMrQ","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"TAB Tipo I → ≥1 episodio maníaco (no requiere depresión para dx)","guid":"QoIEAEJNSnOk3_J6Fgm9mw","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"TAB Tipo II → ≥1 episodio hipomaníaco + ≥1 episodio depresivo mayor (NUNCA manía)","guid":"KVt0NXZVR7qaha6zgTJHoQ","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"5","text":"Ciclotimia → 2 años con hipomanía + depresión subsindromática (sin criterios completos)","guid":"QdOuPGx7RMmRU8pAW9ly4w","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"5","text":"TAB inducido por sustancias/condición médica → clínicamente indistinguible de TAB I primario","guid":"knpGVzYTS_2cilC_usKOAA","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"5","text":"TAB no especificado → incluye episodio mixto, Tipo III (viraje por factor externo)","guid":"bNzbvKc5TYeA2-z5BB7SHg","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"Tipo III: antidepresivos, hormonal, drogas, estrés, lesión cerebral","guid":"_nlDHk4JSbqYcflH5YXUvw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"1","text":"Clasificación CIE-11 → similar, incluye espectro bipolar","guid":"S2TpgeUfRn-i1ANUCSK-5g","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"1","text":"Especificadores DSM-5-TR","guid":"4gNxlTRoQ-e-72weBdmrcw","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"Severidad: leve, moderado, severo","guid":"0xhES0PDSAKjWkT-SyDz5Q","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"Con/sin síntomas psicóticos","guid":"YwIeDWTDTkKhl3kFK3GGgw","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"13","text":"Con características catatónicas, melancólicas, atípicas, peripartum","guid":"C3nmZnB9S9uC5eBA2CRwjg","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"13","text":"Ciclado rápido","guid":"b0vB9FDfTHahGIxyguVE4g","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"13","text":"Con patrón estacional","guid":"ppY-J3ziSl-7wTHI_ngnrA","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"13","text":"Con características mixtas (NUEVO especificador)","guid":"7KUVbYHBRXmYQHWj0k0taA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"3VMYmn4MShK6ZK3lok7hHw","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"Prevalencia general","guid":"DUxtYEubSJSkfGsTCO7Glg","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"TAB I → ~1% población general","guid":"cN3DgyfFQkui7gr5v5gkzA","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"TAB II → 1.5-2.5%","guid":"1ehKziKsSJSP8V3s25KWlQ","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"Espectro bipolar subsindromático → 4-12%","guid":"ycSPd9TgTketsSuZXsHyPw","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"21","text":"Subestimación: solo ~20% de positivos en screening reportan dx previo","guid":"gK1dIMQzQsa245cyfgSjgw","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"20","text":"Prevalencia en adulto mayor (≥65 años)","guid":"v0BsIehuT4iVSz_-3nVC5w","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Comunitaria → 0.08-0.5% (MUCHO MENOR que adulto joven)","guid":"uFK3RaIpSPqtFs4Sdd8DTg","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"Hospitalizados geriátricos → 8-10%","guid":"pWbmE4L9RviCDr6kpvKpuQ","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"Residencias de larga estadía → hasta 10% residentes","guid":"siR7wyw1S5ao_yo5t5noLQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"20","text":"Distribución por sexo → TAB I similar H:M, TAB II más frecuente en mujeres","guid":"NTT8L5cXQAeoqWjMHzUHIQ","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"20","text":"Edad de inicio → típico 15-25 años, 5-10 años hasta inicio de tratamiento","guid":"VUf-HWGYTMS6MuTyFKAnUQ","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"20","text":"Inicio tardío (>50 años) → ~8-29% según cohorte","guid":"_9wna5bnRXaDeREHd0a08g","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"20","text":"Disminución prevalencia con edad → explicaciones","guid":"KgjDJz5-RdmbvYs-Omjz2w","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"Sesgo de participación (AM menos en encuestas)","guid":"hEBFGKrVTaGSfKKQYMHugQ","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"Enmascaramiento por deterioro cognitivo","guid":"KolNzbQAT1aj87LodgBEBg","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"SESGO DEL SUPERVIVIENTE → mortalidad aumentada (HR 1.51, IC 95% 1.28-1.77)","guid":"3TwUvxo2RviYWrP0M9N_uQ","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"33","text":"Institucionalización (no contados en estudios comunitarios)","guid":"cCGPBVlnQx6qLgUHWDa0QA","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"20","text":"Número absoluto de AM con TAB EN AUMENTO por envejecimiento poblacional","guid":"62m51U85TbGeU6P-KQ1E8w","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"0","text":"Genética y Factores de Riesgo","guid":"0BuGMjUoTK6tjQlIKbgj9g","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"HEREDABILIDAD alta → ~80% (estudios en gemelos)","guid":"AWEnwtMhRGK4kTiDEDVnwA","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"39","text":"Antecedentes familiares: TAB, depresión mayor, esquizofrenia","guid":"H4E6WH4IS-u9FfZaKx6YYg","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"39","text":"Genes candidatos: CACNA1C, ANK3, BDNF, CLOCK genes","guid":"PN8o2wlPTbimx9OQg1_ULw","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"39","text":"Factores de riesgo ambientales","guid":"YcI1AGKsS_exdM2a6LNBXw","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"Estrés psicosocial → precipitante de episodios","guid":"JglQ-RD7SY-VTwKu4TfVDw","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"Trauma infantil → mayor riesgo y peor pronóstico","guid":"KcyUI80sTqG3aa6QQmPdQQ","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"43","text":"Uso de sustancias → cannabis, estimulantes","guid":"MOO191xDT7KzhPLnuD3lWQ","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"43","text":"Alteración ritmos circadianos","guid":"z2S4o-WyR2622b1LC4z0rA","children":[]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"39","text":"Inicio tardío: factores específicos","guid":"ggdtu7_7Qou33vWxNS7hNg","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"Patología cerebrovascular → hiperintensidades sustancia blanca","guid":"eePGr-xhTHCabfaLrvlIFA","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"Lesiones hemisferio derecho (ACV, tumores, focos epilépticos)","guid":"nXi3m548QGm2EzK6dHWTtg","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"48","text":"Disrupción circuito orbitofrontal","guid":"rI77bKhbQjOzcvOzk-n1Jw","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"48","text":"Enfermedades neurodegenerativas","guid":"b1DdXTp4SAuQAboJxX0x-A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"0","text":"Neurobiología","guid":"wZXK_J_fTaahhJbcfiP4mw","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"Neurotransmisores","guid":"EkqUZj-lSO2nmn5DiyApwQ","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"Hipótesis monoaminérgica: ↑DA/NE en manía, ↓5-HT en depresión","guid":"YPNIqFocR7KXJPIfWhwjRQ","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"Desregulación glutamato/GABA","guid":"59552UdcTC-4-bms8rzJVw","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"54","text":"Alteración señalización intracelular (GSK-3β, PKC)","guid":"CKDsT919T7SadHqH8d90bQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"53","text":"Neuroimagen","guid":"Nb7b2AbTQ5Sfs_wBXEdqrQ","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"Reducción volumen corteza prefrontal y amígdala","guid":"gaFBC4C7R2SR5VZmWjalag","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"Hiperintensidades sustancia blanca (más en AM y LOBD)","guid":"7MXQ1PINQGmfOtpIXK99aQ","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"58","text":"Disfunción circuitos frontotemporales y frontoestriatales","guid":"fsqu-8-oRsKQ7ao8XeyQtw","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"58","text":"TAB inicio tardío → MAYOR carga lesional sustancia blanca vs inicio precoz","guid":"gdjZFg3CRq24T-_8FMT8Yg","children":[]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"53","text":"Modelo de Kindling → episodios generan vulnerabilidad para episodios futuros","guid":"QZDJxqEwQ6qd5MhPVzLSkA","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"53","text":"Ritmos circadianos","guid":"cAeKoK4oRsyAtxFFOqie0Q","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"Disrupción eje HPA","guid":"98ScdFneTpeAzNu0Jl3pJw","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"Alteración melatonina y CLOCK genes","guid":"0dx0-3xQRu65xsxNeNPAKg","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"Inestabilidad ritmo sueño-vigilia como trigger","guid":"Mitl-OMFRGuWRvA3Yftfxw","children":[]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"53","text":"Neuroinflamación → ↑IL-6, TNF-α, PCR en episodios agudos","guid":"3xchERyRSjKgRlaIrf1gpA","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"0","text":"Episodio Maníaco","guid":"aTFxZFYyR6ihPmZyEtOdlw","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"Criterios DSM-5-TR","guid":"GxEYXUV_RrKty0OTRueO-g","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"A: Ánimo elevado, expansivo o irritable + ↑energía/actividad ≥1 SEMANA","guid":"70wc1VtZSiGzxygN0bfwKA","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"B: ≥3 síntomas (4 si solo irritable) → DIGFAST","guid":"pwzU5cOoQEerDIsIbFUDlA","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"70","text":"C: Deterioro funcional marcado o requiere hospitalización","guid":"T_On5L3_SfWj54v1T6eORw","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"70","text":"D: No atribuible a sustancias ni condición médica","guid":"oRpnac7NQOC1bMuJiS-FZw","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"69","text":"DIGFAST (mnemotecnia)","guid":"oFNEVG-TSNiJkWahCMNSBg","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"D → Distractibilidad","guid":"8ioaKLiHR8ao_KZdPR55pw","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"I → Irresponsabilidad/Impulsividad (actividades riesgosas)","guid":"fW4lMTmaSeSYiY5Pjz4Itw","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"75","text":"G → Grandiosidad/autoestima inflada","guid":"ojYhkPXFSPaAW63KfJHzaQ","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"75","text":"F → Fuga de ideas/taquipsiquia","guid":"zj4IJkYtSiuojjZc9uqYew","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"75","text":"A → Actividad aumentada (dirigida a objetivo o agitación psicomotora)","guid":"ozanocwESh2VbDm9jhvp7g","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"75","text":"S → Sleep decreased (↓necesidad de sueño ≠ insomnio)","guid":"5i2ku_AeQTiewQ8KRwWyRQ","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"75","text":"T → Talkativeness (verborrea, habla presionada)","guid":"neFcNXmqSxK-nZLq6JaO1w","children":[]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"69","text":"Síntomas psicóticos (en manía severa)","guid":"b8XOldT8QoSXnfIsG8i2Qw","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"Ideas delirantes congruentes: grandiosidad, poderes especiales, contenido religioso","guid":"VFlzjeQOTNOrgNL5DwDaBg","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"Ideas paranoides: persecución, trato injusto","guid":"wIpcB1SlSgiDjeFebDRMzw","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"83","text":"Alucinaciones auditivas/visuales","guid":"CWMhNwDKRx-tCdcCGB_IjA","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"83","text":"Ideofugalidad → puede llegar a incomprensible","guid":"dlFyAXzITJuRhGHYEk16pg","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"83","text":"Síntomas catatónicos posibles","guid":"toi6E2r8S3SERlleWT_Qsw","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"83","text":"AUSENCIA de noción de enfermedad (falta de insight)","guid":"kIlDaQbyQrqpVxr3a6NzrQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"69","text":"Curso → inicio puede ser súbito, duración media ~13 semanas","guid":"o2GBkwK5S2ibERxj8Z-YoQ","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"25% resuelve en 4 semanas","guid":"PTl970obT96J9E36II697A","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"50% resuelve en 7 semanas","guid":"KjmqytlDQQ-W2XWEEYE7Og","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"75% resuelve en 15 semanas","guid":"5HQ_fs78Qh-f6H77wL032w","children":[]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"69","text":"Presentación en adulto mayor","guid":"c6cEkreyRP6ed2d2ZDCd_A","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"Episodios maníacos MENOS SEVEROS que en jóvenes","guid":"phyMbvHSRNSfO5znxpmEdw","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"94","text":"Características psicóticas MENOS frecuentes","guid":"K4Og0SO0Q5S0YEvVgL3e6w","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"94","text":"Irritabilidad y disforia > euforia clásica","guid":"Etf9bxyUQ4GFYd0ha_9Ffw","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"94","text":"MAYOR confusión → dx diferencial con delirium","guid":"PVXPErI6SHGDCa-j8FhorA","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"94","text":"Mayor componente cognitivo (disfunción ejecutiva)","guid":"R7JMBoLSQcOJHDYACKDpbQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"0","text":"Episodio Hipomaníaco","guid":"fkIes4YyRMO2n6QXf5Jqvg","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"Criterios DSM-5-TR","guid":"Lj-VMfofQviiNxTwH07SYA","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"Mismo perfil sintomático que manía","guid":"n6izql3KRnODq0wCQ-KM_g","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"Duración ≥4 DÍAS consecutivos","guid":"EAKLHjxUQ263mUC89_DDvQ","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"101","text":"Cambio inequívoco en funcionamiento (observable por terceros)","guid":"GbDq_UqTRBetgWNHVLBTlw","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"101","text":"NO deterioro funcional marcado","guid":"j8bA-ngJQVO7uHyl_a-Q2A","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"101","text":"NO requiere hospitalización","guid":"teazvu42QC6D5EQRkEbHfQ","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"101","text":"NO síntomas psicóticos (si los hay → reclasificar como manía)","guid":"k3t_VkksTCuOYyNZKnd_cw","children":[]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"100","text":"Diferencia clave con manía → grado de deterioro funcional y severidad","guid":"hNwewZUsQ9uhZeN0BVhq-Q","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"100","text":"Frecuentemente subdiagnosticado → pacientes no consultan por sentirse bien","guid":"xxj_Vg8vTGmFGHpWgj-lFQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"0","text":"Episodio Depresivo Bipolar","guid":"Cjv9j4_AQdWfVl2npejRvA","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"Criterios → mismos que episodio depresivo mayor (DSM-5-TR)","guid":"N9jPGe2oST6NoyUnBi6b2A","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"110","text":"Características sugestivas de BIPOLARIDAD (vs depresión unipolar)","guid":"pltIL7uVRpmxlubsZ9LE7w","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"Inicio agudo","guid":"rKvwBScFQkOlF2aK8P49Xg","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"Episodios más frecuentes y severos pero más cortos","guid":"cFqozOJbTSugVkTJYslQ4g","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"Hipersomnia e hiperfagia (depresión atípica)","guid":"RMGx4re8R6iaqe8Fq3MOWA","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"112","text":"Lentitud psicomotora marcada","guid":"UEDMaKPoSs2gFqphyjgVHg","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"112","text":"Síntomas neurovegetativos prominentes","guid":"3nGrPUFfTpWe_qdwuCCpvQ","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"112","text":"Afecto lábil","guid":"LGeLIgS5RLuLfpgSWpMcSA","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"112","text":"Componente psicótico → ideas deliroides de culpa patológica","guid":"uv1wB32CSAubRRfVtJXx-w","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"112","text":"Inicio ≤13 años","guid":"SM83V77bSV6g6768Ijb_cw","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"112","text":"Múltiples episodios depresivos previos","guid":"oNlLri5FTxycLPRWE8qFpw","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"112","text":"Historia familiar de TAB","guid":"Zersxs1ZRQm3ja8AmnCw4w","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"112","text":"Resistencia a antidepresivos","guid":"vPWdq7u_Tb2qprYM4VM8KQ","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"112","text":"Viraje con antidepresivos","guid":"X_OKsyPlTKiMw5cIEZyOBA","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"110","text":"FASE PREDOMINANTE del TAB → pacientes pasan ~50% del tiempo en depresión","guid":"YKqBpH5qR3KHyxGk5Djjgg","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"110","text":"En AM → depresión bipolar es la presentación MÁS FRECUENTE","guid":"VaTc9Z4gSJWbLn8FINmlOw","children":[]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"0","text":"Estados Mixtos","guid":"K0j2rswfR6SMEyr3OXls5w","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"Especificador con características mixtas DSM-5-TR","guid":"Eja0eXBPTGywcOQ2sbQ4Dg","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"Episodio maníaco/hipomaníaco + ≥3 síntomas depresivos simultáneos","guid":"aKdtvkDkTf6A2mdsQWXZHA","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"128","text":"Episodio depresivo + ≥3 síntomas maníacos/hipomaníacos simultáneos","guid":"Z-QdO4iHSZGrZusvz5NifQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"127","text":"Presentación típica","guid":"aehvxSK9RnKqok8hDp35KA","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"Depresión + hiperactividad/verborrea","guid":"9U7mQl5dSGyBEX07kofw_Q","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"Manía + ↓libido/energía","guid":"VrADM1xKQLir-5Cn2j_cpw","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"131","text":"Manía (≠ euforia) + disforia","guid":"tGsJdXYyRR6_K8pB56p4lQ","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"131","text":"Ciclos rápidos manía ↔ depresión en mismo episodio","guid":"YTw7Zu6mRHigniIRUQ_TDg","children":[]}]},{"id":"136","parent":"127","text":"MAYOR RIESGO SUICIDA que episodios puros","guid":"2eaJSN_vQ-2BQyrXVS_Mqg","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"127","text":"Más frecuente en mujeres y AM","guid":"ft25-qkuRuKlhfKxlUi8Xg","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"127","text":"Peor respuesta a litio → considerar valproato","guid":"02GAPebpQ2m5K7anJqbgJA","children":[]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"0","text":"Ciclado Rápido","guid":"HKFR7KZBQfmdtfLJkepnOw","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"Definición → ≥4 episodios afectivos en 12 meses (hipo/manía, depresión, mixto)","guid":"AVdsjGfqSsGCSRbKDCUkpw","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"139","text":"Prevalencia → 10-20% de pacientes con TAB","guid":"0swPDFMkS_i056BvkrQglA","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"139","text":"Factores de riesgo","guid":"RZogaftBR6eATjSzCe0Cxg","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"Sexo femenino","guid":"6JS7bu_1TCqyiZJzmfwrpg","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"142","text":"TAB II > TAB I","guid":"XVl4qn2HR9mKXbeHSBYXpQ","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"142","text":"Hipotiroidismo (subclínico incluido)","guid":"9l9W9USyQg2SsoPExvaRFg","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"142","text":"Uso de antidepresivos (pueden inducirlo)","guid":"iD3BOOHxQhWFkj0wVoHegA","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"142","text":"Abuso de sustancias","guid":"VU07wIDHTamuYIZpV680-A","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"139","text":"En AM → ciclado rápido MÁS FRECUENTE que en jóvenes","guid":"lhbUF8yyTXSVZ3n5osMJsw","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"139","text":"Manejo → suspender antidepresivos, optimizar estabilizador, descartar hipotiroidismo","guid":"YSWet5MxRBqOP3QannDT7g","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"139","text":"Peor pronóstico y menor respuesta a litio","guid":"BWCZ0mdoTxqiUmqmbq-8dg","children":[]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"0","text":"TAB de Inicio Tardío (LOBD, >50 años)","guid":"FW2ognMlQn-tDKwetRrQ7Q","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"Características diferenciales vs inicio precoz (EOBD)","guid":"OPgq-0dlRpq3g78_gXoWjw","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"MENOR carga genética/familiar","guid":"cRnK4nm_RoePg6ErPrImbQ","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"MAYOR asociación con patología orgánica cerebral","guid":"xQJiCTSSRBakwkOc1_B-7A","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"MAYOR carga de hiperintensidades en sustancia blanca (neuroimagen)","guid":"2OWM8R9gRAC51PDc0WQVPw","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"152","text":"MAYOR comorbilidad médica y neurológica","guid":"bImuTnPTQW-jq7O46smNGw","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"152","text":"Presentación menos dramática pero más confusa","guid":"Bz99PSieRbiX0-I7eKryMg","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"152","text":"Mayor componente cognitivo → riesgo de progresión a demencia","guid":"XWfS9JKwT4efBBnhTrlNcQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"151","text":"Manía de inicio tardío → ENFERMEDAD MÉDICA HASTA DEMOSTRAR LO CONTRARIO","guid":"1vJ7iOqGQu2v13yyFV99nQ","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"151","text":"Causas secundarias obligatorias a descartar","guid":"MIqfkd_OQ-y6FCi8V3oJLA","children":[{"id":"161","parent":"160","text":"Neurológicas: ACV, TEC, esclerosis múltiple, Parkinson, epilepsia lóbulo temporal, demencia","guid":"Lua2tc-qSD6VgYUkfToCvQ","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"160","text":"Metabólicas/endocrinas: tirotoxicosis, Cushing","guid":"zaG9xn_mSSOpYF5weVUo_Q","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"160","text":"Infecciosas: VIH, neurosífilis","guid":"ul3KtAEnQliHHsk42h1t1w","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"160","text":"Neoplasias: tumores cerebrales (especialmente hemisferio derecho)","guid":"9-jDapIvR3Cg20wF5bqeWw","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"160","text":"Fármacos: corticoides, L-DOPA, estimulantes, antidepresivos","guid":"NRQz0dldRmqDBkGMT7PMOg","children":[]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"151","text":"Neuroimagen OBLIGATORIA → RM cerebro como estándar","guid":"LNY_fjKgT8KXR_ZIAAFNsw","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"151","text":"Correlato neuroanatómico → lesiones hemisferio derecho, circuito orbitofrontal","guid":"ciqG06BWQ5a4wrUJ_SLBzw","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"151","text":"Dx diferencial CRÍTICO","guid":"dnxvhyHcSMaIo0o1y71HGg","children":[{"id":"169","parent":"168","text":"Delirium hiperactivo → SIEMPRE descartar primero","guid":"eoAJpY_cT2mmS1FX46nU9Q","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"168","text":"Demencia con síntomas conductuales (DFTvc, DCL)","guid":"Io1cKDKJTNK0asfX4uaXgg","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"168","text":"Depresión con agitación","guid":"bPlFtXhVQA664zxhd8FmmA","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"168","text":"Efectos adversos de fármacos","guid":"UVzFYKk2Tg2b9oweXwXz9A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico Diferencial","guid":"GeA9GbWcTg25v6rUBE3iIQ","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"Esquizofrenia → síntomas psicóticos NO congruentes, deterioro crónico, ánimo plano","guid":"VN9gkqc7SV61IUiH295ixw","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"Trastorno esquizoafectivo → síntomas psicóticos persisten SIN episodio anímico","guid":"qByOboTaRMGA_Auijrhqqw","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"173","text":"Depresión unipolar → sin historia de (hipo)manía, sin viraje","guid":"eReoRUiyQaSe0VjOs3sxhQ","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"173","text":"TDAH → crónico desde infancia, sin episodicidad, sin grandiosidad","guid":"NhVSzL4RTAGUJKvOpBYJcw","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"173","text":"Trastorno de personalidad límite → inestabilidad crónica, no episódica, reactividad interpersonal","guid":"b-FUDoPnS46M3L3uL9B9Qw","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"173","text":"Delirium → fluctuante, inatención, causa orgánica aguda, reversible","guid":"2ATzr5UbQ1insoMRQSMwrg","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"173","text":"Demencia con síntomas psiquiátricos → deterioro progresivo, no episódico","guid":"HFaW-_6kTICvzsYEKWXRkA","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"173","text":"Hipertiroidismo → descartar con TSH","guid":"9WBvSEvYS6O3AoC_nXvQZQ","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"173","text":"Abuso de sustancias → estimulantes, cannabis, alcohol","guid":"-5urua_MQ-2cmeh2Vmgr-A","children":[]}]},{"id":"183","parent":"0","text":"Escalas de Evaluación","guid":"nlfKK9IQRzauX7JN3D3bSA","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"Screening hipomanía/manía","guid":"NL771iP3QqSCzdqjfIchVQ","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"MDQ (Mood Disorder Questionnaire) → autorreporte, 13 ítems, sensibilidad ~70%","guid":"y4tTspiwSbCqPA1fs4QExg","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"184","text":"HCL-32 (Hypomania Checklist) → 32 ítems, mejor sensibilidad para TAB II","guid":"sET_NgonQsu4_OaL0tLv2w","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"184","text":"BSDS (Bipolar Spectrum Diagnostic Scale)","guid":"ByGoEYd7QBmPaKvhfqBebg","children":[]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"183","text":"Severidad manía","guid":"rNh2hu7RRQazbDbW9qx2_Q","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"YMRS (Young Mania Rating Scale) → 11 ítems, gold standard, VALIDADA en AM","guid":"3ERiJeUiTBG-n0uhGhOJhg","children":[]}]},{"id":"190","parent":"183","text":"Severidad depresión","guid":"Y0-WJTY1Qgy5CEEVR0GABg","children":[{"id":"191","parent":"190","text":"PHQ-9 → screening y seguimiento","guid":"tb1fB2BMRc-OKSoa5thGhg","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"190","text":"MADRS → más sensible a cambio","guid":"HjTwAUnuSUGXj5qyEzAC9g","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"190","text":"HAM-D → clásica","guid":"NspYfo4rSgOqvmkOPHiSXQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"194","parent":"183","text":"Funcionalidad y cognición","guid":"WGfL0BFCTqeje4KPd67bKw","children":[{"id":"195","parent":"194","text":"FAST (Functioning Assessment Short Test)","guid":"jDqC4KwlSDucGdfd_LSsFQ","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"194","text":"Evaluación neuropsicológica formal si sospecha deterioro cognitivo","guid":"g8IUYP14SK2vj_K0Xybt3Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento Farmacológico","guid":"BP4Zug8IQpiuxOzIWaoKIA","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"PRINCIPIOS GENERALES EN AM","guid":"s5YhjfsjRDyVFFYeSzM0KA","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"Start low, go slow (pero no go nowhere)","guid":"KxjGStD_T7msXDjtQDfbSg","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"Monitoreo frecuente de efectos adversos","guid":"nN28idemTdmnIjcEIkc_zA","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"198","text":"Considerar función renal y hepática SIEMPRE","guid":"qwBo73yPRVKR7vplQxqbNQ","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"198","text":"Revisar interacciones (polifarmacia frecuente)","guid":"U9wVyPqXTY2fZMmFIi8Eiw","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"198","text":"Carga anticolinérgica → minimizar","guid":"01jKgRO7R_iAoIPias03wg","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"198","text":"STOPP/START aplicar","guid":"wRQl3yG4Skua1QPXPsor1g","children":[]}]},{"id":"205","parent":"197","text":"Estabilizadores del ánimo","guid":"wh2VFf1fRhSRY0QgDwkmpA","children":[{"id":"206","parent":"205","text":"LITIO","guid":"mO9JLp16RTeDQKBIl9zJbw","children":[{"id":"207","parent":"206","text":"Primera línea manía y mantenimiento","guid":"Hvm9E6mSS6aX4CAwNNX7Ig","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"206","text":"Rango terapéutico estándar: 0.8-1.2 mEq/L","guid":"ZEZKZwRWTV6SbHLbZ4Yyqw","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"206","text":"RANGO EN AM: 0.4-0.8 mEq/L (MENOR ventana terapéutica)","guid":"5Vp6pMeyTeKKE-VHUQ6vjQ","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"206","text":"Inicio en AM: 150-300 mg/día, titular lentamente","guid":"AGRKlIj0T5q_Et4_oF7BOw","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"206","text":"Monitoreo obligatorio","guid":"neP2X21mRQy5XwPOplUa9A","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"Litemia cada 5-7 días hasta estabilizar, luego cada 3-6 meses","guid":"Tjj8FgJTTcix1k1srinDPA","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"211","text":"Función renal (creatinina, VFG) → nefrotoxicidad crónica","guid":"dwMuW-wBTpKqYVYEociqtw","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"211","text":"TSH/T4L cada 6 meses → hipotiroidismo 20-30%","guid":"3dT0XKzIRSiP01LLioidjg","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"211","text":"Calcio/PTH → hiperparatiroidismo","guid":"d9X6Ce-lQWijQ56qbcYnWQ","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"211","text":"ECG basal → bradicardia sinusal, alteraciones conducción","guid":"n6zFzI5ISvOW8j9WE0ithw","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"211","text":"Peso, glicemia","guid":"78v4ylB5Se6cnR7xrt2PKA","children":[]}]},{"id":"218","parent":"206","text":"Toxicidad → ESTRECHO margen terapéutico","guid":"QQStbJmLQomceIeBYeol-g","children":[{"id":"219","parent":"218","text":"Leve (1.5-2.0): temblor grueso, náuseas, diarrea, somnolencia","guid":"2AIYetqbSc2IPgBhcMA1Dw","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"218","text":"Moderada (2.0-2.5): confusión, ataxia, disartria, fasciculaciones","guid":"wSgRcb0wReC-K5swKAMKuw","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"218","text":"Severa (>2.5): convulsiones, coma, arritmias, muerte","guid":"XS-geZ1VTS6ec4MKwccJvA","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"218","text":"EN AM: toxicidad puede ocurrir CON NIVELES NORMALES","guid":"UoCMKAXqQf6qEIRVsVtoNA","children":[]}]},{"id":"223","parent":"206","text":"Interacciones CRÍTICAS en AM","guid":"FSVB5VpASyqhbAbpS5DcHw","children":[{"id":"224","parent":"223","text":"AINEs → ↓excreción renal litio → TOXICIDAD","guid":"67CwN2ssS_GUBWnGKMrF8A","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"223","text":"IECA/ARA II → ↓excreción renal litio","guid":"s9fC1VT9Rqe-XP4PGLMTaw","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"223","text":"Tiazidas → ↓excreción renal litio (↑litemia 25-40%)","guid":"k87Vm_27QaONj0YNDL_Ytg","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"223","text":"Diuréticos de asa → menor efecto pero vigilar","guid":"xUasS2iCTi-lWoGYgh_QgA","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"223","text":"Metformina → monitorear función renal","guid":"XuoYv2IsQOq9A3JPca5ZEw","children":[]}]},{"id":"229","parent":"206","text":"Diabetes insípida nefrogénica → poliuria, polidipsia, amiloride como tratamiento","guid":"jPqtbfegSAmYvtHuTZO8ZQ","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"206","text":"Efecto neuroprotector potencial → ↓riesgo demencia (controversia)","guid":"G1wWvkS9T0ilYygg70GeKg","children":[]}]},{"id":"231","parent":"205","text":"Ácido valproico (divalproato)","guid":"m2mK76SURVyLRMpXNTrexw","children":[{"id":"232","parent":"231","text":"Alternativa a litio especialmente en estados mixtos y ciclado rápido","guid":"xwXipadDQ-aQNJUQIoHS_Q","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"231","text":"Rango terapéutico: 50-100 μg/mL","guid":"XRzJ-avpQ3mQWqObMxrMPg","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"231","text":"EA en AM: temblor, sedación, aumento peso, trombocitopenia","guid":"WIFLMgB-Re6JUwqoZ2UEKg","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"231","text":"Hepatotoxicidad → monitorear función hepática","guid":"tFHUZc-wRXquitau_0AXlw","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"231","text":"Hiperamonemia → incluso con niveles normales de valproato","guid":"GwuuMyO1SGCP7hbjiES4SQ","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"231","text":"Interacciones: warfarina, lamotrigina (↑niveles)","guid":"Q57QAaKYQtSEmiP1WD5j_w","children":[]}]},{"id":"238","parent":"205","text":"Carbamazepina","guid":"9DmPjwulRnWpKWkdk6RsAQ","children":[{"id":"239","parent":"238","text":"Segunda-tercera línea","guid":"sR26cv2ZQBqEIi-pnoxb_Q","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"238","text":"Inductor enzimático potente (CYP3A4) → MÚLTIPLES interacciones","guid":"KxLOLHqCTRWQKPBRzDCE_g","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"238","text":"EA: hiponatremia (SIADH), agranulocitosis, Steven-Johnson","guid":"qBun3ao6SuSK9j11yBo6jg","children":[]},{"id":"242","parent":"238","text":"Poco usado en AM por perfil de interacciones","guid":"Jobohm1LSPqhzAUmo3o9Yw","children":[]}]},{"id":"243","parent":"205","text":"Lamotrigina","guid":"LH0RfgspSUqZnN9CAtyEog","children":[{"id":"244","parent":"243","text":"PRIMERA LÍNEA en depresión bipolar y mantenimiento (prevención depresión)","guid":"OBEChCLqT4CPRShXagIfuw","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"243","text":"NO eficaz para manía aguda","guid":"nwL9l9s8ROSY6pFcZC7UDA","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"243","text":"Titulación LENTA obligatoria → riesgo Stevens-Johnson/NET","guid":"Af9G4k48QFaZHurRILn-Zw","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"243","text":"Inicio 25 mg/día × 2 sem → 50 mg × 2 sem → 100 mg → max 200 mg","guid":"5qoI41oVRe6FphbGL5o4rw","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"243","text":"Si uso concomitante valproato → titular a MITAD de velocidad","guid":"FxoFL9vnRpGl3ngirfPclw","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"243","text":"Bien tolerada en AM → buen perfil EA","guid":"74M1CZ43SsSpYHKEjBTvlg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"250","parent":"197","text":"Antipsicóticos atípicos","guid":"XHtkElMnStSlShl8ssEQnA","children":[{"id":"251","parent":"250","text":"Quetiapina","guid":"5WACbnP2SRGB0Un16JEAyQ","children":[{"id":"252","parent":"251","text":"Aprobada para manía, depresión bipolar y mantenimiento","guid":"tokPkEw3RBeaSVuA3-A6mg","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"251","text":"Dosis manía: 400-800 mg/día (en AM iniciar 25-50 mg)","guid":"sJkB6mG7RVu_jUGyy0Jzgg","children":[]},{"id":"254","parent":"251","text":"Dosis depresión bipolar: 300 mg/día (en AM 50-150 mg)","guid":"9nXF8lpCTUKnkBEWRnYJKg","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"251","text":"EA: sedación, hipotensión ortostática, síndrome metabólico","guid":"qFBcrF68T12tXpTW9fyduw","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"251","text":"MUY USADO en AM por efecto sedante y ansiolítico","guid":"NHlR07KpQUuGit3ZipmWLA","children":[]}]},{"id":"257","parent":"250","text":"Olanzapina","guid":"2mmXM7ZIQLGqqPAcNbEtdg","children":[{"id":"258","parent":"257","text":"Eficaz en manía aguda","guid":"xsIPDUgUQnaROB2LRGMwnw","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"257","text":"EA LIMITANTE en AM: aumento peso, síndrome metabólico, sedación","guid":"vpovpwFxS0aKJgAnVvY1Ug","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"257","text":"Olanzapina/fluoxetina → aprobada depresión bipolar (pero ↑riesgo metabólico)","guid":"3EilgKdkRmGSYtE22a0lHA","children":[]}]},{"id":"261","parent":"250","text":"Aripiprazol","guid":"vDarKnOFQbaxnpdAUc-WPw","children":[{"id":"262","parent":"261","text":"Agonista parcial D2/5-HT1A","guid":"MOWe4oNEQACWmVN-lGpSVw","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"261","text":"Menor riesgo metabólico que olanzapina/quetiapina","guid":"DXLrXndVRneooTc042qaVA","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"261","text":"EA: acatisia (frecuente en AM), insomnio","guid":"fC9HC8hLRJiQ1I5XU9sDuA","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"261","text":"Dosis AM: iniciar 2-5 mg","guid":"tP_yrG59T06nIfHp0i927A","children":[]}]},{"id":"266","parent":"250","text":"Lurasidona","guid":"QvUdywGbTLufPTrA7-ApRQ","children":[{"id":"267","parent":"266","text":"Aprobada depresión bipolar (monoterapia o adyuvante)","guid":"H-DRmnebRXiM1jDTQ5_qDA","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"266","text":"BUEN perfil metabólico → sin aumento peso significativo","guid":"DlJmQ71CStC_RP2kt2nMaQ","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"266","text":"Tomar con alimento (≥350 kcal para absorción)","guid":"F0OeeRqjR8qEAzYtQuSiIA","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"266","text":"Dosis AM: 20-80 mg","guid":"UqQq_oKZR6KPhSAt_Xfqvw","children":[]}]},{"id":"271","parent":"250","text":"Cariprazina","guid":"escRs-e_R0yZVEuRvCbjZQ","children":[{"id":"272","parent":"271","text":"Agonista parcial D2/D3","guid":"MmrL_k4eSY6dLt7Y-Yu2Ig","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"271","text":"Aprobada manía y depresión bipolar","guid":"AE0dd4sCTF-jRciivekIWQ","children":[]},{"id":"274","parent":"271","text":"Vida media ULTRA LARGA (~2-4 semanas metabolito activo)","guid":"97pbdxp8TTGzp5-ybj-LcA","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"271","text":"Precaución en AM por acumulación","guid":"CI3Sa9NyS26LxYarOuGBpQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"276","parent":"197","text":"Manejo por fases","guid":"OhqDUXaKSmKfl4sKNK0Lvw","children":[{"id":"277","parent":"276","text":"Manía aguda","guid":"W4YOzbvvTNyC5nQ21tO7hA","children":[{"id":"278","parent":"277","text":"Primera línea: litio O valproato ± antipsicótico atípico","guid":"EYkGSoYtQXqIscEvFW7EhA","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"277","text":"Si severa/psicótica: antipsicótico atípico + estabilizador","guid":"2x9a-OgRQyud-LMItzf5yw","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"277","text":"Suspender antidepresivos","guid":"cx5SmUO9TIuNSMabygEmXQ","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"277","text":"Hospitalización si riesgo auto/heteroagresión","guid":"wL2gAWpaRvShSGp2GuCI0A","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"277","text":"EN AM: preferir valproato o quetiapina sobre litio si ERC o múltiples interacciones","guid":"-xBmq0CPT2SxDjzF11zJwg","children":[]}]},{"id":"283","parent":"276","text":"Depresión bipolar aguda","guid":"9EOPhZEgQ8Szyqv34Qo6Dw","children":[{"id":"284","parent":"283","text":"Primera línea: quetiapina monoterapia O lamotrigina O lurasidona","guid":"vz71FyDAT2qkthduGKnxrA","children":[]},{"id":"285","parent":"283","text":"EVITAR antidepresivos en monoterapia → riesgo viraje","guid":"_yJV0lmISD-FdBbI4VEXlg","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"283","text":"Si antidepresivo necesario → ISRS (sertralina, escitalopram) + estabilizador","guid":"QOXb6zVBQ4KCWx12a7edjw","children":[]},{"id":"287","parent":"283","text":"NUNCA tricíclicos ni venlafaxina → mayor riesgo viraje","guid":"b_KOr6Q3SK-3tC9PQv5z7g","children":[]}]},{"id":"288","parent":"276","text":"Mantenimiento","guid":"hWxfG8YfQb6VWJl-LQeeQQ","children":[{"id":"289","parent":"288","text":"Litio → previene manía > depresión, efecto antisuicida","guid":"S4d7B-B3Sian7s7D0zoTrw","children":[]},{"id":"290","parent":"288","text":"Lamotrigina → previene depresión > manía","guid":"N8YHaY8JT72T_UKb0-XBzg","children":[]},{"id":"291","parent":"288","text":"Valproato → mantenimiento si respondió en fase aguda","guid":"_VMl88AVR_CaTWH9HVXE1Q","children":[]},{"id":"292","parent":"288","text":"Quetiapina → previene ambos polos","guid":"0PimwXHrR4anIczBJaDZsg","children":[]},{"id":"293","parent":"288","text":"Combinaciones frecuentes: litio + lamotrigina, litio + quetiapina","guid":"obEQVfkJQ1WO860gaxYEVA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"294","parent":"197","text":"Consideraciones geriátricas farmacológicas","guid":"7NZi8LskROudRxNnSjGGZQ","children":[{"id":"295","parent":"294","text":"Farmacocinética alterada: ↓VFG, ↓albúmina, ↓masa hepática → ↑fracción libre","guid":"eFT8oA-JRNWI8ZeKxBiwZg","children":[]},{"id":"296","parent":"294","text":"Dosis iniciales 25-50% menores que adulto joven","guid":"7Dx1BCA2QHGJ_DxyO6yY3A","children":[]},{"id":"297","parent":"294","text":"Titulación más lenta","guid":"VMDco-_YR22kdMpH4MB5kQ","children":[]},{"id":"298","parent":"294","text":"Monitoreo más frecuente de niveles y EA","guid":"AlpyKrUjTYKRs18rHU_MWw","children":[]},{"id":"299","parent":"294","text":"Revisar Beers/STOPP-START","guid":"eh3TX8VaTNCyiveGqyCZzQ","children":[]},{"id":"300","parent":"294","text":"DEPRESCRIPCIÓN: evaluar necesidad de cada fármaco en cada visita","guid":"YtE0GrVoRHa5POqy1tP9hg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"301","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento No Farmacológico","guid":"lO_RS6AlQAyM2EehBlnSLA","children":[{"id":"302","parent":"301","text":"Psicoeducación → piedra angular, incluir familia/cuidadores","guid":"wFUEL0iMTVarhsO369QKMg","children":[]},{"id":"303","parent":"301","text":"TCC adaptada para TAB → prevención de recaídas, adherencia","guid":"5u6H3xuXSjKYo68GoZgBrw","children":[]},{"id":"304","parent":"301","text":"Terapia de ritmos sociales (IPSRT) → estabilización rutinas y ritmos circadianos","guid":"RLdatkOSTJ2d-VsT-rrfWg","children":[]},{"id":"305","parent":"301","text":"Terapia electroconvulsiva (TEC)","guid":"VEo-c7cOT_6uVhIp3FXyrg","children":[{"id":"306","parent":"305","text":"Indicada en manía refractaria, depresión severa refractaria, catatonia","guid":"t8GtrDEmRsa5HIj-D8gnWQ","children":[]},{"id":"307","parent":"305","text":"SEGURA y eficaz en AM → considerar como opción válida","guid":"Odn8SnflRM6-LTS3_UtJrw","children":[]},{"id":"308","parent":"305","text":"Precaución: deterioro cognitivo transitorio","guid":"cmXpq4FwQeen6VoZbfj7hA","children":[]}]},{"id":"309","parent":"301","text":"Intervenciones sobre sueño → higiene, regulación horaria","guid":"pM4rbGauTa2ozrKxEagEtg","children":[]},{"id":"310","parent":"301","text":"Ejercicio regular → evidencia creciente en estabilización anímica","guid":"V7VnqWIbRqCqYQurqCLTtQ","children":[]},{"id":"311","parent":"301","text":"Rehabilitación cognitiva si deterioro presente","guid":"cIH6N6OYStK8CNcnDeFstw","children":[]}]},{"id":"312","parent":"0","text":"Comorbilidades","guid":"xq9YbZhASu6owWr0WMkUIg","children":[{"id":"313","parent":"312","text":"Psiquiátricas","guid":"1oNwIyl1QrayNDni-kUh6w","children":[{"id":"314","parent":"313","text":"Trastornos de ansiedad (TAG, pánico) → hasta 50%","guid":"kWbCdFvXRpG5SUlWuYOuFQ","children":[]},{"id":"315","parent":"313","text":"Abuso de sustancias (alcohol, cannabis) → 30-50%","guid":"nyYdys6rTV2j_gy87OMIEQ","children":[]},{"id":"316","parent":"313","text":"TDAH → frecuente sobreposición","guid":"77kFfqT_TaCIc9oDa3g7NA","children":[]},{"id":"317","parent":"313","text":"Trastorno de personalidad","guid":"Q_xStOEYQk2X8gSU9hPIBg","children":[]}]},{"id":"318","parent":"312","text":"Médicas (especialmente en AM)","guid":"5GrqdStLSGC2vk3SMOs-gQ","children":[{"id":"319","parent":"318","text":"Cardiovascular → HTA, cardiopatía coronaria, IC (litio: bradicardia)","guid":"OaHzdNTzTaeU-5MYml-a5A","children":[]},{"id":"320","parent":"318","text":"Metabólico → DM2, obesidad, dislipidemia (asociados a antipsicóticos)","guid":"bmXN60XCReupQoHUcjpspg","children":[]},{"id":"321","parent":"318","text":"Endocrino → hipotiroidismo (litio), síndrome metabólico","guid":"bHzq17nYRWiDOU723jycKg","children":[]},{"id":"322","parent":"318","text":"Neurológico → deterioro cognitivo, riesgo de demencia (OR ~2-3)","guid":"4jV-t5OXQPWx3zkJ-dZs_g","children":[]},{"id":"323","parent":"318","text":"Renal → ERC (litio crónico → nefropatía tubulointersticial)","guid":"gipbI05aTNixV2_Q4QcCzw","children":[]}]},{"id":"324","parent":"312","text":"Deterioro cognitivo asociado a TAB","guid":"suuQj9ApTSaEzes6je9Zag","children":[{"id":"325","parent":"324","text":"Presente incluso en eutimia (déficit ejecutivo, atención, memoria verbal)","guid":"9poXe8rQRiypMUeyM23Ccg","children":[]},{"id":"326","parent":"324","text":"Progresivo con número de episodios (modelo kindling)","guid":"l7WgeJedSECfBiDpOvkFBA","children":[]},{"id":"327","parent":"324","text":"TAB como factor de riesgo independiente para demencia","guid":"jxy0i6-pTAWZMVR7jwf57Q","children":[]},{"id":"328","parent":"324","text":"En AM: difícil diferenciar de DCL o demencia incipiente","guid":"aL7Irso-Tue-GbZQIOWAdQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"329","parent":"0","text":"Pronóstico y Seguimiento","guid":"622kf6RSRim-hsCcH0_iUw","children":[{"id":"330","parent":"329","text":"TAB es condición CRÓNICA con recurrencias","guid":"jbfT5JroTjOjJ3FDwzjVDw","children":[]},{"id":"331","parent":"329","text":"Factores de mal pronóstico","guid":"eKd1OlJgT9WW8QVx6lKQnQ","children":[{"id":"332","parent":"331","text":"Mayor número de episodios previos","guid":"kQXuQnkpQbqgJtxB4u3EKQ","children":[]},{"id":"333","parent":"331","text":"Ciclado rápido","guid":"os60mHzNSn-LJDResMYVVA","children":[]},{"id":"334","parent":"331","text":"Comorbilidad médica y psiquiátrica","guid":"TTA7ISDZTgGS8x37Cn_RIw","children":[]},{"id":"335","parent":"331","text":"Abuso de sustancias","guid":"Vx3gywKxQp-_hlg30uPwLQ","children":[]},{"id":"336","parent":"331","text":"No adherencia al tratamiento","guid":"Q5nZARzhQJukXP1VR8ZIuQ","children":[]},{"id":"337","parent":"331","text":"Inicio tardío con patología cerebral","guid":"Q9q8rTT4QiapU8DtW13qSA","children":[]}]},{"id":"338","parent":"329","text":"Seguimiento en AM","guid":"v8Cp6X-LQEeSLNlDv0lSfA","children":[{"id":"339","parent":"338","text":"Control psiquiátrico cada 1-3 meses","guid":"WcCo5w_pSjuyDkwTXD18ng","children":[]},{"id":"340","parent":"338","text":"Monitoreo de litemia/niveles cada 3-6 meses","guid":"jj71QG7aT4yRqts5L0VVOw","children":[]},{"id":"341","parent":"338","text":"TSH, función renal, perfil metabólico cada 6-12 meses","guid":"Tp2vbW3_Rwi5iHMF4PfA7Q","children":[]},{"id":"342","parent":"338","text":"Evaluación cognitiva anual (MoCA/MMSE)","guid":"nyxTPFW_RoKWJEEDw75zfA","children":[]},{"id":"343","parent":"338","text":"Screening cardiovascular periódico","guid":"hmiQhRWZQkuimZGdEoCnAA","children":[]},{"id":"344","parent":"338","text":"Evaluación funcional (Barthel, Lawton) en cada visita","guid":"Uc73MXp0RZ2wY-_6PoaqYA","children":[]}]},{"id":"345","parent":"329","text":"Mortalidad → aumentada vs población general","guid":"CwzAt7cBT32yPh9J33jhtA","children":[{"id":"346","parent":"345","text":"Suicidio → TAB tiene MAYOR tasa de suicidio entre trastornos afectivos","guid":"iLttADMJSDyOiNekbsXmuQ","children":[]},{"id":"347","parent":"345","text":"Litio → único fármaco con evidencia de EFECTO ANTISUICIDA","guid":"-jOxMxyXQLiGgSGDqr8Idw","children":[]},{"id":"348","parent":"345","text":"Causas cardiovasculares y metabólicas","guid":"Jqc4JRFkT5C-05RVSI9tkA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"349","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas","guid":"AeYOXHaHSea9_LLftdAf7A","children":[{"id":"350","parent":"349","text":"Manía tardía (>50 años) = ENFERMEDAD MÉDICA hasta demostrar lo contrario → RM cerebro obligatoria","guid":"hOLL4PRgTnu1XMRXWmRe0g","children":[]},{"id":"351","parent":"349","text":"En AM: litemia terapéutica 0.4-0.8 mEq/L → toxicidad puede ocurrir con niveles normales","guid":"B3HUj6-cTDKygciuq1Okug","children":[]},{"id":"352","parent":"349","text":"DIGFAST para recordar criterios de manía (Distractibilidad, Irresponsabilidad, Grandiosidad, Fuga ideas, Actividad, Sleep ↓, Talkativeness)","guid":"clA7qJ28TwCWEjDdc3ka4Q","children":[]},{"id":"353","parent":"349","text":"Depresión bipolar ≠ depresión unipolar → NUNCA antidepresivo en monoterapia","guid":"jIuxdmGxToS_MAr7oadm9Q","children":[]},{"id":"354","parent":"349","text":"Tricíclicos y venlafaxina → MAYOR riesgo de viraje que ISRS","guid":"hvOpfyZUSuyDU920Ow3kNg","children":[]},{"id":"355","parent":"349","text":"Lamotrigina → titular LENTO (riesgo Stevens-Johnson), ideal para prevenir depresión bipolar","guid":"sKhSwrNYRFChISNxsjSKog","children":[]},{"id":"356","parent":"349","text":"Litio → ÚNICO fármaco con efecto ANTISUICIDA demostrado","guid":"HVZr_DmDSKGl4bkOtYhNqw","children":[]},{"id":"357","parent":"349","text":"AINEs + litio → combinación potencialmente LETAL en AM (↑litemia)","guid":"LKW8z0GmQ1ezUilE_KDhEA","children":[]},{"id":"358","parent":"349","text":"IECA + tiazidas + litio → triple amenaza para toxicidad por litio","guid":"QXnNUzpmSneajAgJXIi1jQ","children":[]},{"id":"359","parent":"349","text":"En AM con ERC: preferir valproato o quetiapina sobre litio","guid":"bikUzRNmScqPVHSiVHSDfQ","children":[]},{"id":"360","parent":"349","text":"Ciclado rápido: SUSPENDER antidepresivos y descartar hipotiroidismo","guid":"f2SPxRBoRlqp28riR98yEg","children":[]},{"id":"361","parent":"349","text":"TAB es factor de riesgo INDEPENDIENTE para demencia → seguimiento cognitivo anual","guid":"KQleWCrNTBu9aCZwmDAMNw","children":[]},{"id":"362","parent":"349","text":"YMRS validada en población geriátrica → usar para monitoreo de manía","guid":"vBVLPQ81QMi503kgk6Ip-Q","children":[]},{"id":"363","parent":"349","text":"Quetiapina: único fármaco aprobado para los 3 usos (manía, depresión bipolar, mantenimiento)","guid":"RI5rycKCQ-eGKqu5Hvj5lA","children":[]},{"id":"364","parent":"349","text":"En AM con TAB, siempre evaluar: función renal, tiroidea, cognitiva, cardiovascular y funcional","guid":"3AuimHSFTpK__KFHZjimOg","children":[]},{"id":"365","parent":"349","text":"Referencias","guid":"HgRtU3_xQpuG5R9EhcFd-Q","children":[{"id":"366","parent":"365","text":"1. Shobassy A. Elderly Bipolar Disorder. Curr Psychiatry Rep. 2021;23(5):5.","guid":"B2_Khl1LSaS7fjiixyatCQ","children":[]},{"id":"367","parent":"365","text":"2. Sajatovic M, et al. Bipolar disorder in older adults. J Nerv Ment Dis. 2015;203(11):866-71.","guid":"KrDQJinORkusMCITDDVzHQ","children":[]},{"id":"368","parent":"365","text":"3. Dols A, et al. Older age bipolar disorder. Psychogeriatrics. 2021;21(5):651-61.","guid":"wV_GLnErQZ2IZtc8cloYKQ","children":[]},{"id":"369","parent":"365","text":"4. Cipriani A, et al. Lithium in the prevention of suicide. Am J Psychiatry. 2005;162(10):1805-19.","guid":"Dk0U2fRVSlWMYoKyfBjTfg","children":[]},{"id":"370","parent":"365","text":"5. Yatham LN, et al. CANMAT/ISBD guidelines for bipolar disorder. Bipolar Disord. 2018;20(2):97-170.","guid":"cI0XFL_URqSgEuzxMK_ItQ","children":[]},{"id":"371","parent":"365","text":"6. Stahl SM. Essential Psychopharmacology. 4th ed. Cambridge; 2013.","guid":"En4sPOY5SaG9MYepHcQ5hQ","children":[]},{"id":"372","parent":"365","text":"7. American Psychiatric Association. DSM-5-TR. Washington, DC: APA; 2022.","guid":"czWfDJ73Rh6tFgm0Am6eXg","children":[]},{"id":"373","parent":"365","text":"8. Jalil J, et al. Depression, Anxiety, and Other Mood Disorders. En: Geriatric Psychiatry.","guid":"wU1KTW9JQNKrc2wGCwQ_GA","children":[]},{"id":"374","parent":"365","text":"9. Young RC, et al. YMRS. Br J Psychiatry. 1978;133:429-35.","guid":"vKo8GYiqQo6TllltdCx2Og","children":[]},{"id":"375","parent":"365","text":"10. Post RM. Kindling and sensitization in bipolar disorder. Clin Neurosci Res. 2007;2:365-76.","guid":"FbLzwj0fQSaNrcTt3eJOew","children":[]},{"id":"376","parent":"365","text":"11. Aziz R, et al. Late-onset bipolar disorder. Am J Geriatr Psychiatry. 2006;14(2):101-8.","guid":"zEPlo75-Qly9xi7YXJFdXg","children":[]},{"id":"377","parent":"365","text":"12. Depp CA, et al. Bipolar disorder in older adults. Clin Psychol Rev. 2004;24(5):507-24.","guid":"Sqo-IRQdSbOxHix5d61e7Q","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":377,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Psiquiatría","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Psiquiatría","filename":"Trastorno_Afectivo_Bipolar_TAB","id":"map_2178","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Trastorno_Afectivo_Bipolar_TAB"}